Package model

Class Appointment

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Appointment
  • public class Appointment
extends java.lang.Object
    The Appointment class simulates an Appointment. It allows for data to be held about the appointment, as well as an associated User ID, Customer ID, and Contact ID.
    Version:
    1
    Author:
    Mary Williams
